# Google OAuth Client ID — required for Drive integration.
#
# How to get one:
#   1. Go to https://console.cloud.google.com
#   2. Create a project (or select existing)
#   3. APIs & Services → Enable "Google Drive API"
#   4. Credentials → Create → OAuth 2.0 Client ID → Web application
#   5. Add your dev URL to "Authorised JavaScript origins":
#        http://localhost:3000
#      (add your production URL too when you deploy)
#   6. Copy the Client ID below
#
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your value:
VITE_GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=your_client_id_here.apps.googleusercontent.com
